lead_paragraph: Senior Jaysean Paige and Daxter Miles Jr. each scored 15 points and No. 10 West Virginia closed out its home regular season on senior night Wednesday by trouncing Texas Tech 90-68.

headline.print_headline: No. 10 West Virginia Routs Texas Tech on Senior Night
